channel.title: Model help for PI
channel.description: Iv heard that the models for delta and PI are different or is it just the ints that are different? If this is true can you please tell me how to convert into PI from delta?

item.title: Model help for PI
item.dc:creator: @Dharma Dharma
item.description:
@Dharma wrote:

Questions about models belong in the client help section, right? I’m pretty sure the models are not different. It’s just the ints I think and you’ll find them in different files. In Pi I think it’s in itemdef and Delta it’s in class8.java. Post this in the client section. you’ll get a better answer.
